Arduino program to generate NMEA sentences for opencpn from MPU 6050 data.

// based on http://www.giuseppecaccavale.it/arduino/mpu-6050-gy-521-arduino-tutorial/
// and https://kingtidesailing.blogspot.com/2015/09/how-to-make-nmea-0183-tilt-compensated.html

EXAMPLE OF SENTENCE ACCEPTED BY OPENCPN
$IIXDR,A,-2.6,D,PTCH,A,-12.5,D,ROLL*6E<0x0D><0x0A>

Wiring:
MPU 6050    ARDUINO UNO
VCC -------> 3.3v
GND -------> GND
SCL -------> ANALOG A5
SDA -------> ANALOG A4
